OL,6,FAn accountant who stole more than
OL,7,F#330,000 from his firm out of "greed"
OL,8,Fto fund a holiday home and a Range
OL,9,FRover has been jailed.
OL,11,FLaurence Hearldon, 39, from , , stole
OL,12,Fthe money from Sanjeev 1979 Ltd,
OL,13,Fsecretly transferring money 140 times
OL,14,Finto his account for nearly three
OL,15,Fyears.
OL,17,FThe father who was described as a
OL,18,F'liked' and 'trusted' employee said he
OL,19,Fhad begun making the fraudulent
OL,20,Ftransactions after falling into debt.
