OL,6,FBut heard he had bought a Range Rover
OL,7,Fand a 'holiday home' in .
OL,9,FHearldon was sentenced to three years
OL,10,Fin prison after pleading guilty to an
OL,11,Foffence of committing fraud by abusing
OL,12,Fhis position.
OL,14,FHe was sacked from his position as a
OL,15,Fsenior managing clerk at a
OL,16,F'successful' Cheetham Hill based
OL,17,Fwholesale fashion company when his
OL,18,Fcrime was discovered.
