OL,6,F"These purchases prove that the only
OL,7,Fexplanation for your offending is
OL,8,Fgreed," Judge Sarah Johnston told him.
OL,10,F"I'm also entirely satisfied from
OL,11,Feverything that I have read and heard
OL,12,Fthat the majority of your offending
OL,13,Fwas to provide a lifestyle beyond your
OL,14,Fmeans."
OL,16,F"You were liked and you were trusted,"
OL,17,Fthe judge continued.
OL,19,F"You have lost your good character by
OL,20,Fvirtue of this offence. You have let
OL,21,Fyour family down very badly."
