OL,6,FProsecuting, William Donnelly said
OL,7,FHearldon joined the firm in May 2014.
OL,9,F"By all accounts he was viewed as a
OL,10,Fpopular and diligent member of the
OL,11,Faccounting department," he said.
OL,13,FHe was promoted to the role of senior
OL,14,Fmanaging clerk in August 2021, which
OL,15,Finvolved access to "all areas of the
OL,16,Fcompany's financial affairs".
