OL,6,FMr Donnelly said the firm's turnover
OL,7,Fwas 'running into the tens of millions
OL,8,Fof pounds annually', adding that a
OL,9,F'small part' of the company's business
OL,10,Fwas conducted via the PayPal payment
OL,11,Fsystem.
OL,13,FConcerns about a discrepancy was
OL,14,Fraised after an audit of the company's
OL,15,Ffinances was carried out in 2021.
OL,17,FHearldon tried to 'explain it away'
OL,18,Fwhen he was first questioned by
OL,19,Fcompany bosses, but he confessed after
OL,20,Fbeing confronted again.
