OL,6,F"It seems that the company's PayPal
OL,7,Faccount was being used as a personal
OL,8,Faccount by Mr Hearldon to extract sums
OL,9,Fof money which were not
OL,10,Finsubstantial," Mr Donnelly said.
OL,12,FHe was 'summarily dismissed', and
OL,13,Fattended a voluntary interview with
OL,14,Fpolice.
OL,16,FHearldon told officers that he started
OL,17,Fto steal 'small amounts' after getting
OL,18,Fin debt but had then 'lost control'.
OL,19,FHe has since paid back #43,000 of the
OL,20,Fmoney stolen.
