OL,6,F"He is a man who wishes, perhaps for
OL,7,Fthe goodness of his redemption, to be
OL,8,Fable to pay back to the community,"
OL,9,Fthe barrister added.
OL,11,F"It is a sad story of a man who saw an
OL,12,Fopportunity to help feather the nest,
OL,13,Fbut kept going with it."
OL,15,FBut Judge Johnston said the offence
OL,16,Fwas too serious for any punishment
OL,17,Fother than an immediate prison
OL,18,Fsentence.
